<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Área Privada</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h2>Bem-vindo, {{usuario.usuario}}!</h2>
        <p>Você acessou uma área protegida contendo três fotos do Sung Jin-woo do anime Solo Leveling.</p>

        <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/assets/solo1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/assets/solo2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/assets/solo3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Anterior</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Próximo</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-danger mt-3">Sair</a>
    </div>

</body>

</html>